{
  "name": "00 Mailjet - Importación BBDD a Postgres (v12)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🗺️ Arquitectura general\n\n**Fase 1** — Delta sync de contactos:\nDetecta cambios por actividad email (`LastActivityAt`) + contactos nuevos.\nSync completa automática: domingos · `force_full=true` · contactos nuevos.\n\n**Fase 2** — Listas Mailjet:\n- Delta ≤ 500 contactos → `/contact/{id}/getcontactslists` (rápido)\n- Delta > 500 o sync completa → paginación `/listrecipient` completa\n\n**Retry:** todos los HTTP 5×5s · batchInterval 1500ms\n**Limit:** 1000 registros/request\n\nCredenciales: siempre desde el gestor de credenciales de n8n.\n⚠️ Antes de la primera ejecución ejecutar ALTER TABLE (ver doc externa).",
        "height": 220
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        25152,
        976
      ],
      "id": "f6774d3d-d551-448d-bc73-92b8fc9e1781",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "SELECT COUNT(*) AS pg_count, MAX(last_sync) AS last_sync FROM contactos",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "5544c63d-467a-47f0-a056-e9a2c0c27ea6",
      "name": "Postgres GET MAX last_sync",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.6,
      "position": [
        27296,
        1408
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": {
          "id": "kF6UjQ8hguq0ltLd",
          "name": "Postgres - n8n-whatsapp"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Convierte MAX(last_sync) de Postgres a Unix timestamp.\n// Incluye pg_count para detectar contactos nuevos en Mailjet.\n// Fuerza sync completa (ts=0):\n//   - Los domingos (garantía de consistencia semanal)\n//   - Si force_full=true en el Manual Trigger (forzado manual)\nconst raw     = $input.first().json.last_sync;\nconst pgCount = Number($input.first().json.pg_count ?? 0);\n\nconst esDomingoSync = new Date().getDay() === 0;\n\n// Lee force_full del Manual Trigger solo si fue él quien disparó la ejecución.\n// Con workflowInputs (typeVersion 1.1), el valor llega en .json directamente.\nlet forceFull = false;\ntry {\n  const manualNode = $('When clicking \\'Execute workflow\\'');\n  if (manualNode.isExecuted) {\n    forceFull = Boolean(manualNode.first()?.json?.force_full ?? false);\n  }\n} catch(e) {\n  forceFull = false;\n}\n\nconst ts = (raw && !esDomingoSync && !forceFull)\n  ? Math.floor(new Date(raw).getTime() / 1000)\n  : 0;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    last_sync_unix: ts,\n    pg_count:       pgCount,\n    force_full:     forceFull,\n    ts_inicio:      Date.now(),\n    fecha_inicio:   new Date().toISOString()\n  }\n}];\n"
      },
      "id": "9b059443-1a4a-44e7-a5df-185dfecab6c7",
      "name": "Code Preparar Contexto",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        27520,
        1408
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://api.mailjet.com/v3/REST/contact",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "mailjetEmailApi",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "CountOnly",
              "value": "1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "a85d399d-8f03-4ecc-837f-5601efb19a99",
      "name": "HTTP Conteo Total Mailjet",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        27744,
        1504
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 5,
      "waitBetweenTries": 5000,
